function Start()
	local tAdds = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_Cellar_Adds")
	local tCaps = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_Capn_Cellar")
	for i, actorID in ipairs(tAdds) do
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(actorID, false)
		Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(actorID, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(actorID, false)
	end
	for i, actorID in ipairs(tCaps) do
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(actorID, false)
		Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(actorID, true)
		--Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(actorID, false)
	end	
	
	--enable  deserter
	local actorDeserter = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_04_Cellar_Deserter")[1]
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorDeserter)
	
	--move deserter into place (using two markers so he doesn't get stuck)
	local marker = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_04_Cellar_Convo")[1]
	local markerDogleg = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_04_Cellar_Dogleg")[1]
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorDeserter, markerDogleg, "NPC_Walk_Fast", false)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorDeserter, marker, "NPC_Walk_Fast", false)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorDeserter, marker)
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(actorDeserter, "QST_Penitent_Fight")
	
	
end

--get references
	local markerDeserterPost = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_Deserter_Cellar_Post")[1]
	local deserter = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_04_Cellar_Deserter")[1]
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	--do prayer convo and wait for it to finish
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(convPrayer, deserter)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(deserter, convPrayer)
	--move deserter to position for final convo
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(deserter, markerDeserterPost, "NPC_Walk_Fast", false)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(deserter, markerDeserterPost)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(deserter)
	Hydra.EventSend("QST_Penitent_04 _Fight_End")

function Start()
	local tAdds = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_Cellar_Adds")
	local tCapsNonCombat = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_Capn_Cellar")
	local tCapsCombat = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_Capn_Cellar_Combat")
	for i, actorID in ipairs(tAdds) do
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(actorID, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(actorID, false)
		Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(actorID, true)
	end
	for i, actorID in ipairs(tCapsCombat) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(actorID)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(actorID, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(actorID, false)
		Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(actorID, true)
	end	
	for i, actorID in ipairs(tCapsNonCombat) do
		Hydra.ActorDisable(actorID)
	end		
end
